      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUCKLE UP MENZIE (1) has a strong record here with three wins and two placings from six starts. Comes off a (30.25) win last time, scoring by one length in a Grade 5 over 515m at this track. Expected to go close. CANYA LEXI (2) goes very well here including two wins. In the money last time at Hobart (26.37) in a Grade 4, finishing a 9 length third. Makes strong appeal on best. BROOKDENE (3) turned in a solid run last start over 461m at Hobart finishing 5th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (26.25). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Likely to be about the mark. FIRE WATER BURN (6) placed last start in slick time and is in the mix again.",
